my ad showing pending for a lon time

If your ad is pending for a long time, it might be due to your account not being verified yet. Could you please provide the following details so we can assist you further?

- Company's full address
- Company's legal entity name
- Account Email
- Company's EHID or DUNS number
- Primary contact person's name
- Company's phone number
- Business URL

Once you have this information, please email it to adsupport@newsbreak.com with the subject line: Business Verification. This will help us conduct a thorough review and update you on your account status.

Thanks for confirming that your account is verified. Since your ad is still pending, it might be due to other factors. Ads are typically reviewed within 4 hours on weekdays and up to 8 hours on weekends. If it's been longer than that, please double-check your ad content for compliance with our guidelines.

If everything seems in order and the ad is still pending, you can reach out to adsupport@newsbreak.com for further assistance.
